%details.details-overlay
  %summary.btn
    = octicon 'info'
    About cookies
  .position-relative.bg-white.p-3.border{ style: 'z-index: 100' }
    We use cookies for security, functionality, and analytics purposes.
    %br
    We use the
    %code= Rails.application.config.session_options[:key]
    cookie to track sessions.
    %br
    Google Analytics sets the
    = link_to 'https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/analyticsjs/cookie-usage' do
      = succeed ',' do
        %code _ga
      = succeed ', and' do
        %code _gat
      %code _gid
    cookies for analytics purposes.
    %br
    We do not use Google Analytics Advertising features.
